{"id":"59863f27-c5d5-45ea-ab9f-888336994b95","name":"Number 9 | Reversed Role","description":"<p>He thought losing his job on Christmas Eve was the peak of his bad luck—until he heard a broken whimper echoing from the shadows of a rotting building. Inside, he found you—someone who had been through hell and back and was clearly still trapped there.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SwHEfzLBDTASNCbjojN-a.webp\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 44, 128); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 44, 128); color: inherit;\">𝐀𝐔𝐓𝐇𝐎𝐑'𝐒 𝐍𝐎𝐓𝐄</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 44, 128); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\">First of all… I’m back. Like, actually back. After a whole month. And you know what? My dear stalker, you’re just a  bitch. :3 But my dears, I missed you all so much. If I manage to finish my ST cards today, I swear I’ll bring you more and more boys. Every. Single. Day. (I hope 😞❤️)</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\">In this bot, you can be anyone you want, in any setting you like. Something terrible may have happened — you could be Number 9, abandoned… basically, any scenario you can roleplay. Even something like a demi-human who ended up in the human world. Sounds interesting, right? You’re free to choose anything you want and create completely new rps.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SwHEfzLBDTASNCbjojN-a.webp\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 44, 128); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 44, 128); color: inherit;\">𝐀𝐋𝐓𝐄𝐑𝐍𝐀𝐓𝐈𝐕𝐄 𝐒𝐂𝐄𝐍𝐀𝐑𝐈𝐎𝐒</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 44, 128); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img sr